OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'It's everywhere' - how    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FHamas attack haunts        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FIsrael's student soldiers  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The first time I crossed into Gaza     
OL,6, through the Erez checkpoint in 1991 it 
OL,7, was not much more than a few bored     
OL,8, Israeli soldiers in a shed, checking   
OL,9, IDs, before they let visitors drive    
OL,10, their cars through an opening in the   
OL,11, barbed wire and into Gaza.             
OL,13,FIn the years since then, it evolved    
OL,14,Finto a gleaming terminal, with complex 
OL,15,Flayers of concrete walls, defences and 
OL,16,Fsteel gates, all covered with dozens of
OL,17,FCCTV cameras. Only the very trusted and
OL,18,Fprivileged were allowed to drive       
OL,19,Fthrough Erez. Journalists had to walk  
OL,20,Fand drag their bags with them.         
